### 2.4 Discovery Manifests (Beyond JSON-RPC)

**`.well-known/mcp.json`** (optional, for server discovery):
```json
{
  "servers": {
    "my-tool-server": {
      "type": "stdio",
      "command": "/path/to/server",
      "args": []
    }
